LITON TECHNOLOGY said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 44.11% to NT$133,607,000 from NT$239,051,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            133,607          239,051    
YOY%             -44.11%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            695,961          977,150    
YOY%             -28.78% 
=================================================================
 